(671, 60, 'first_visit_text', ' <p> Please arrive 15 minutes prior to your appointment time to fill out the necessary paperwork. Remember to bring your insurance card and prescription for physical therapy (if you have one). Please be sure to wear comfortable, nonrestrictive clothing since your initial evaluation will typically involve exercises - shorts for knee injuries, sports bra for women with shoulder injuries. Sneakers or similar footwear is also suggested. </p>\r\n      <p> During your first visit, your physical therapist will evaluate your injury and discuss an appropriate plan of treatment. This will include what interventions will be used, expected outcomes, and the duration and frequency of required treatment. </p>'),
