(957, 68, 'hand_therapy_text_right', ' <h3 class="text-center list-heading">Treatment techniques we offer:</h3>    <ul class=ul-centered>       <li>Deep Tissue Massage</li>       <li>Range of Motion Exercises </li>       <li>Strengthening Exercises </li>       <li>Electrical stimulation</li>       <li>Ultrasound</li>       <li>Cryotherapy</li>       <li>Wound and Pin Care </li>       <li>Pain Management</li>       <li>Scar and Edema Management </li>       <li>Ergonomic Recommendations</li>       <li>Joint Protection Techniques</li>       <li>Customized Splinting</li>    </ul>'),
