(1999, 91, 'about_space', '<p> We are located in the           <strong>          <a href="http://www.elysiumfitness.net/" target=_blank>Elysium Fitness Club</a>          </strong> at 117 West 72nd Street, 2nd Floor. Elysium Fitness Club is a private trainer fitness gym providing personal training, massage and nutritional counseling. We have state of the art Cybex, Free Motion and cardiovascular machines, as well as private treatment rooms and locker rooms with showers.        </p>'),
